OL,3,CMPs accuse Royal Mail of 'lying' and
OL,4,C'pretending' not to prioritise parcels
OL,6,FMPs have accused Royal Mail of "lying"
OL,7,Fabout its performance and "pretending"
OL,8,Fnot to prioritise parcels over letters.
OL,10,FIt comes after concerns Royal Mail is
OL,11,Fnot meeting Ofcom targets for
OL,12,Ftimeliness in its deliveries,
OL,13,Fpotentially leading to millions of
OL,14,Fletters arriving late.
OL,16,FLabour MP Dave Robertson said people
OL,17,Fin his constituency are "sick of being
OL,18,Flied to by Royal Mail".
OL,26,@nD@`OUnD@fO]oD@[OUoD@fO]yD@YOUzD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
