OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773267087
OL,3,CMPs accuse Royal Mail of 'lying' and
OL,4,C'pretending' not to prioritise parcels
OL,6,FThe Lichfield MP said on Wednesday: "I
OL,7,Fmet Royal Mail just before Christmas
OL,8,Fto complain to them about the total
OL,9,Flack of a postal service that we have
OL,10,Fin Lichfield. We were probably the
OL,11,Fworst area in the country at that
OL,12,Fpoint.
OL,14,F"I was told when I had that meeting
OL,15,Fthat all of the first class mail went
OL,16,Fout that week. That is a lie, it is an
OL,17,Fabsolute lie, because my constituents
OL,18,Ftold me. Royal Mail clearly don't have
OL,19,Fa handle on this ` they are either not
OL,20,Fmeasuring their performance or they
OL,21,Fare covering up their performance."
OL,26,@nD@eOUvD@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
