OL,3,CMPs accuse Royal Mail of 'lying' and
OL,4,C'pretending' not to prioritise parcels
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FHe called on the government to force
OL,12,FRoyal Mail to "be honest, 'fess up and
OL,13,Ffix it".
OL,15,FBusiness minister Blair McDougall said
OL,16,Fhe understands how "frustrating" it is
OL,17,Ffor MPs to "raise a problem and be
OL,18,Ftold that it doesn't exist".
OL,26,@tD@OOUuD@GO]xD@TOUxD@`O]yD@LOUzD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
