OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773267087
OL,3,CMPs accuse Royal Mail of 'lying' and
OL,4,C'pretending' not to prioritise parcels
OL,6,F"Royal Mail have a responsibility
OL,7,Fabsolutely to address that in a direct
OL,8,Fand straightforward manner, because if
OL,9,Fwe aren't recognising the problem,
OL,10,Fwe'll not deal with it," he added.
OL,12,FSeveral MPs alleged Royal Mail
OL,13,Fprioritises parcels, contributing to
OL,14,Fthe late delivery of letters and
OL,15,Fleading to some customers missing
OL,16,Fimportant information, such as medical
OL,17,Fappointments.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@XO]
