OL,3,CMPs accuse Royal Mail of 'lying' and
OL,4,C'pretending' not to prioritise parcels
OL,6,FIn a letter published this week by the
OL,7,FCommons Business and Trade Committee,
OL,8,Fchief executive Alistair Cochrane said
OL,9,FRoyal Mail does not "operate a general
OL,10,Fpolicy of prioritising parcel
OL,11,Fdeliveries over letters".
OL,13,FHe said delivering parcels before
OL,14,Fletters was only prioritised during
OL,15,Fbusy periods like Christmas to avoid
OL,16,Fthem overcrowding delivery offices,
OL,17,Fbut admitted the company does not keep
OL,18,Fspecific data on the number of letters
OL,19,Fde-prioritised for parcels during
OL,20,Fthese periods.
OL,26,@qD@UOUsD@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
