OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773267087
OL,3,CMPs accuse Royal Mail of 'lying' and
OL,4,C'pretending' not to prioritise parcels
OL,6,FLiberal Democrat MP Jess Brown-Fuller
OL,7,F(Chichester) said the blame for
OL,8,Ffailures "doesn't lie with postal
OL,9,Fworkers" who are "doing all they can
OL,10,Fto deliver a service".
OL,12,F"But it lies with a private company
OL,13,Fthat is telling their staff to
OL,14,Fprioritise parcels and then pretending
OL,15,Fthat that's not their policy.
OL,16,FConstituents in my area of Chichester
OL,17,Fhave received hospital appointments
OL,18,Ffour days after the appointment was
OL,19,Fdue to take place," she said.
OL,26,@tD@AOU{D@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
