PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F313A1773267087
OL,3,CMPs accuse Royal Mail of 'lying' and
OL,4,C'pretending' not to prioritise parcels
OL,6,FLabour MP Ian Lavery (Blyth and
OL,7,FAshington), who had raised the urgent
OL,8,Fquestion on the matter, said Royal
OL,9,FMail's denial over operating a parcels-
OL,10,Ffirst policy was "contradicting
OL,11,Frepeated internal testimonies" and
OL,12,F"flies in the face of local evidence
OL,13,Ffrom the workforce".
OL,15,FIt is "a standing joke that the
OL,16,Fquickest way to get a letter delivered
OL,17,Fis to put it inside of a parcel",
OL,18,FLabour MP Lee Barron (Corby and East
OL,19,FNorthamptonshire) said.
OL,26,@uD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
