OL,3,CMPs accuse Royal Mail of 'lying' and
OL,4,C'pretending' not to prioritise parcels
OL,6,FResponding, Mr McDougall said: "On the
OL,7,Fissue of the prioritisation of
OL,8,Fparcels, Ofcom had examined this a few
OL,9,Fyears ago and had found that there
OL,10,Fwasn't evidence of it as a policy
OL,11,Fcentrally.
OL,13,F"But I've heard from so many members'
OL,14,Fstories about the prioritisation of
OL,15,Fparcels, and so it's something I
OL,16,Fintend to raise with Ofcom later this
OL,17,Fafternoon."
OL,26,@nD@`OUuD@AOUyD@KO]
